      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Send camera video at 480p instead of 720p for smoother streaming</li><li>New screen share resolution menu icon</li><li>Make screen sharing exclusive: starting a share takes it over from your pair</li><li>Add shared-code peers: call across any network without Tailscale (P2P hole punching)</li><li>Show what changed in the update dialog and GitHub release notes</li><li>Add rendezvous server for shared-code calls, deployed automatically from CI</li></ul>]]></description>
